en_184872_0	Met Department says that showers or thundershowers will occur at times in the Uva province and in Batticaloa, Ampara, Polonnaruwa and Hambantota districts.
en_184872_1	Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places elsewhere except in Northern province, particularly after 2 pm, it says.
en_184872_2	Heavy falls (about 100 mm) can be expected at some places in Western and Sabaragamuwa provinces and in Galle, Batticaloa and Ampara districts.
en_184872_3	There may be temporary localized strong winds during thundershowers.
en_184872_4	General public is kindly requested to take adequate precautions to minimize damages caused by lightning activity.
